{"tid":1720457,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大學校長：「如無犯罪證據！不能進入校園，若有學生流血，我將以死相搏！」　警察：「若有流血，我自殺。」","createTime":"2019-11-14T11:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T11:16:12.000Z","uid":14328,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07a47d556ce9ad8379ad7f848db7a7e2d33a7b60","tid":1720457,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:03:03.000Z","msg":"正值50年前<br />\n<br />\n1949年4月6號。當年國共戰火連年，有傳共匪偷偷進入台大避難，當時台大校長，傅斯年確實有警告警察總司彭孟緝：「若有證據該抓就抓，若無證據就不能隨便進學校抓學生！我有一個請求，你今天晚上驅離學生時，不能流血，若有學生流血，我要跟你拚命！」，而彭孟緝則回應：「若有人流血，我便自殺。」<br />\n<br />\n反觀當今位高權重之人，何以全為匪類？"},{"pid":"20edb242a196586849ae5702f476483f1ca8fa86","tid":1720457,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:05:30.000Z","msg":"有呢個覺悟<br />\n唔該辭職<br />\n我地對校長既期望應該係咁"},{"pid":"d09768d27d1de3468dfaa459a5d97bd73fb9fa43","tid":1720457,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇呢個覺悟<br />\n唔該辭職<br />\n我地對校長既期望應該係咁</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4fe594eb26c4eb1562e456d1e096953d1db2bfa5","tid":1720457,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:06:41.000Z","msg":"校長唔做就全香港人做"},{"pid":"6ac92cdee9d5a0479313789f51cf27cebe12074f","tid":1720457,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bf8aa674ebbc51bf7afa11ac6cf824f8423450","tid":1720457,"uid":136182,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:07:20.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post 再諗起城大郭位<br />\n我屌你老母"},{"pid":"185d0928a9391fb89af99ff008d7133c5a377eab","tid":1720457,"uid":14328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67bf8aa674ebbc51bf7afa11ac6cf824f8423450","tid":1720457,"uid":136182,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:07:20.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post 再諗起城大郭位<br />\n我屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11: